headline: FIS to Report Fourth Quarter Earnings on February 24, 2026
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., February 09, 2026--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial services technology, will announce fourth quarter 2025 financial results on Tuesday, February 24th, prior to market open.
